options.query:
| makeresults count=24
| streamstats count
| eval showavail=24
| eval cnsp = "cnsp-" + count 
| eval cnsp_n = "cnsp-n-" + count 
| eval cnsp_s = "cnsp-s-" + count 
| eval cnsp_t_n = "cnsp-t-n-" + count 
| eval cnsp_t_s = "cnsp-t-s-" + count 

| eval alert_level = if(count<=showavail,round(((random() % 5.2)/(5.2)) * (5.2 - 1) ,0) + 10 ,99)
| eval isnorth = if(count<=showavail,round(((random() % 2.2)/(2.2)) * (2.2 - 1) ,0),0)
| eval issouth = if(count<=showavail,if(isnorth=1,0,1) ,0)
| eval alert_n = if(count<=showavail,if(isnorth=1,alert_level+10,0) ,99)
| eval alert_s = if(count<=showavail,if(issouth=1,alert_level,0),99)

| rename count as Number 
| table Number cnsp alert_n alert_s isnorth issouth cnsp_n cnsp_s cnsp_t_n cnsp_t_s item alert showavail
``` numbers ```
| appendpipe 
    [| where isnull(item) 
    | eval item = cnsp
    | eval alert = if( Number<=showavail,1,0)]
    ```blocks North``` 
| appendpipe 
    [| where isnull(item ) 
    | eval item = cnsp_n 
    | eval alert = alert_n ]
    ```blocks South``` 
| appendpipe 
    [| where isnull(item ) 
    | eval item = cnsp_s 
    | eval alert = alert_s ] 
    ```track North ``` 
| appendpipe 
    [ | where isnull(item ) 
    | eval item = cnsp_t_n 
    | eval alert = isnorth ]
    ```track south ``` 
| appendpipe
